             was indicted for <rs id="t18191201-42-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18191201-42-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18191201-42-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18191201-42-cd240" type="crimeDate">13th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-42-off239 t18191201-42-cd240"></join>, 9 lbs. of beef, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18191201-42-victim528" type="victimName">
                     Quinton 
                     Gale
                  <interp inst="t18191201-42-victim528" type="surname" value="Gale"></interp>
